<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id4cda0084-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d" identifier="/us/usc/t34/s10726"><num value="10726">§ 10726.</num><heading> Rules and regulations</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Director of the Bureau of Justice Assistance shall promulgate such rules and regulations as are necessary to carry out this subchapter, including rules and regulations for submitting and reviewing applications under <ref href="/us/usc/t34/s10725">section 10725 of this title</ref>.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id4cda0085-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d">(<ref href="/us/pl/90/351/tI/s3036">Pub. L. 90–351, title I, § 3036</ref>, as added <ref href="/us/pl/115/76/s3/a">Pub. L. 115–76, § 3(a)</ref>, <date date="2017-11-02">Nov. 2, 2017</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/131/1249">131 Stat. 1249</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
